<languages/> {{Infobox dungeon |name = Liberty Garden |image = [[File:Liberty Garden.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Liberty Garden. |tokens = 136,500 |location = Below Unova Route 20 }} '''Liberty Garden''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Unova]]. It initially has 81 tiles arranged in an 9x9 square, including 9 chest tiles, 21 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 2,703,000 HP.
